	measure 'Previous Data Date' = ```
			
			VAR CurrentTaskCode = SELECTEDVALUE('01 XER_TASK'[task_code])
			VAR CurrentDataDate = MAX('01 XER_TASK'[data_date])
			VAR PreviousDataDate =
			    CALCULATE(
			        MAX('01 XER_TASK'[data_date]),
			        FILTER(
			            ALL('01 XER_TASK'),
			            '01 XER_TASK'[task_code] = CurrentTaskCode &&
			            '01 XER_TASK'[data_date] < CurrentDataDate
			        )
			    )
			RETURN
			    PreviousDataDate
			
			```
		formatString: General Date
		lineageTag: 5694209f-6ac6-4f8f-bbdf-4d4eabb4269d

